Package: hsical
Title: Hyperspectral Image Calibration Tool
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mateusz", "Zarowka", , email = "mateusz@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny application for calculating pixel resolution from 
    hyperspectral test scans. Determines length and field-of-view resolution 
    in micrometers per pixel and checks for square pixel geometry.
